# Cloudflare Tunnel token · paste your token here, rename file to .env
#
# Where to get it:
#   1. Open Cloudflare Zero Trust: https://one.dash.cloudflare.com/
#   2. Networks → Tunnels → Create a tunnel
#   3. Type: Cloudflared · Name: swarmbee-nas-bakery
#   4. Install connector → choose Docker
#   5. Copy the long string after "--token" (starts with eyJ...)
#   6. Add a Public Hostname:
#        Subdomain: dl
#        Domain:    swarmandbee.ai
#        Type:      HTTP
#        URL:       nginx:80
#
# Keep this file OUT of git. The actual .env is in .gitignore.

TUNNEL_TOKEN=eyJ...paste-your-token-here...
